- [x] I have read the documentation and made sure this feature doesn't already exist.

comment.body:
Just realised you can also do this:

```js
import got from 'got';
import {CookieJar} from 'tough-cookie';

const cookieJar = new CookieJar();
const sessionGot = got.extends({cookieJar});
```

Would still be nice if I didn't have to create the cookie jar myself.

